name: Admin user is logged in and opens the form for editing meal category "Meal category for edit"

testSteps.description: Given Admin user, ROLE_ADMIN, tries to login

children.description: Admin should see header profile button that is displayed

testSteps.description: And Admin user is on meal categories page

children.description: Admin opens the Meal categories page

testSteps.description: When Admin clicks on Edit button for Meal category for edit with id 10

children.description: Admin clicks on web element located by .mealCategoryEdit-10

testSteps.description: Then Admin should be redirected to Edit page for meal category

children.description: Admin should see a value that is equal to: <"http://localhost:3000/mealCategories/edit/10">

testSteps.description: And Admin should see that name field has value "Meal category for edit" and imageUrl has value "https://i.pinimg.com/originals/c9/c2/b1/c9c2b12a2b325f0080a1f328a0963341.jpg"

children.description: Then meal category name should be 'Meal category for edit'
Then meal category imageUrl should be 'https://i.pinimg.com/originals/c9/c2/b1/c9c2b12a2b325f0080a1f328a0963341.jpg'
